title: The art and architecture of India - Buddhist, Hindu, Jain (Art E
description:
The Art and Architecture of India - Buddhist, Hindu, Jain
Penguin Books | 1984 | ISBN: 140561021 | English | 518 pages | PDF | 87.8 MB


For scholarship, readability, and the range of its illustrations The Pelican History of Art has come to be recognized as a unique enterprise in the field of art history. More than thirty volumes have already appeared in a work which is planned to cover the art and architecture of all ages in about fifty volumes. Written by authorities whose international standing is unquestioned, they have notably maintained the strict standards set by the Editor, Sir Nikolaus Pevsner
